Drawcord waistband. Machine wash. Imported

name: Nike Tech Colorblock
description:
Layer Up and Play On!

Let your kids say 'Hello!' to adventure with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Hoodie. Crafted from premium lightweight fleece, this hoodie offers all the warmth without the bulk to keep your kids ready to take on the day. The smooth fabric feels fantastic both inside and out, while the signature Tech Fleece look shines through with stylish taping and seam details. With a handy zippered pocket, there's secure storage for your kiddos' snacks and secret mission essentials. Watch your kids turn every day into an opportunity to play with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Hoodie.

Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Hoodie Features:

  • Body: 53% cotton/ 47% polyester; Hood lining: 69% cotton/31% polyester
  • Taping and seam details
  • Zippered pocket
  • Side hand pockets
  • Cuffs finished with a smooth, stretchy binding
  • Machine wash
  • Imported

description:
Elevated Basic

Experience what an icon feels like with the Nike Sportswear Cargo Pants. Bring classic sophistication to your daily rotation with the Nike Sportswear Cargo Pants.

  • Water-repellent finish
  • Woven twill
  • Elastic waistband with an internal drawcord
  • Roomy cargo pockets with snap-button closures
  • Elastic cuffs
  • Machine wash
  • Imported

Get eco-friendly warmth and comfort on the go with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers. The iconic paneled design and articulated knees offer that unmistakable Tech Fleece vibe you love, while tapering from the knee to ankle provides a fitted look, so you flaunt your sneakers with confidence.

name: Nike Tech Fleece
description:
Fleece Flair

Get eco-friendly warmth and comfort on the go with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers. Featuring a mix of recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers for a touch of sustainability, these premium fleece joggers feel smooth and warm without the bulk. The signature streamlined fit delivers a sleek, tailored look. The iconic paneled design and articulated knees offer that unmistakable Tech Fleece vibe you love, while tapering from the knee to ankle provides a fitted look, so you flaunt your sneakers with confidence.

Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers Features:

  • Body: 53% cotton/47% polyester; pocket bag knuckle side: 100% cotton
  • This product is made with at least 50% sustainable materials, using a blend of both recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers. The blend is at least 10% recycled fibers or at least 10% organic cotton fibers.
  • Imported
  • Streamlined Fit
  • Elastic waistband with an outer drawcord
  • Taped pocket with an interior organizer
  • Nike Futura logo at the left thigh
  • Tapering from the knee to ankle
  • Ribbed cuffs
  • Machine wash

name: Nike Tech Fleece
description: Say hello to Tech Fleece! Our premium, lightweight fleece—smooth both inside and out—gives you plenty of warmth without adding bulk. These trousers are an easy win you can count on to stay comfy in the cold. Benefits: We evolved our size range to focus on fit, not gender, to let every kid play their way. Stash your snacks and essentials securely in the zip pocket. The taping details on the zip provide the signature Tech Fleece look. Extra fabric between the legs gives you more room to run, jump and stretch. Product details: Body: 53% cotton/47% polyester. Pocket Bag Knuckle Side: 100% cotton. Printed Futura logo. Drawcord waistband. Machine wash. Imported

These trousers are an easy win you can count on to stay comfy in the cold. Benefits: We evolved our size range to focus on fit, not gender, to let every kid play their way. Stash your snacks and essentials securely in the zip pocket. The taping details on the zip provide the signature Tech Fleece look. Extra fabric between the legs gives you more room to run, jump and stretch. Product details: Body: 53% cotton/47% polyester. Pocket Bag Knuckle Side: 100% cotton. Printed Futura logo. Drawcord waistband. Machine wash. Imported

name: Nike Tech Fleece
description:
Fleece Flair

Get eco-friendly warmth and comfort on the go with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers. Featuring a mix of recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers for a touch of sustainability, these premium fleece joggers feel smooth and warm without the bulk. The signature streamlined fit delivers a sleek, tailored look. The iconic paneled design and articulated knees offer that unmistakable Tech Fleece vibe you love, while tapering from the knee to ankle provides a fitted look, so you flaunt your sneakers with confidence.

Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers Features:

  • Body: 53% cotton/47% polyester; pocket bag knuckle side: 100% cotton
  • This product is made with at least 50% sustainable materials, using a blend of both recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers. The blend is at least 10% recycled fibers or at least 10% organic cotton fibers.
  • Imported
  • Streamlined Fit
  • Elastic waistband with an outer drawcord
  • Taped pocket with an interior organizer
  • Nike Futura logo at the left thigh
  • Tapering from the knee to ankle
  • Ribbed cuffs
  • Machine wash
